.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, almond-milk, 7up, cola, coffee
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, japanese, french, thai, british, colombian
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the japanese##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the thai##1
 3. the british is on the right of the french##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the thai##1
 5. the dutch is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the french is between the person drinking soy-milk and the british##2
 7. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 8. the french is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the indonesian##1
10. the dutch is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | 7up  | almond-milk  | mirinda  | coffee      | cola       | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | thai | french | british | colombian | dutch | japanese | indonesian  |

