.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: indie, country, soul, pop, r&b, trance, techno
The people use 7 different means of transport: trike, taxi, car, airplane, jet-ski, snowmobile, subway
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan of country##1
3. the person driving the trike is between the fan of techno and the fan of indie##2
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of indie##1
7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person driving the taxi is the fan of pop##1
9. the fan of r&b is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | r&b | indie | soul | techno      | country      | trance |
| Transport     | taxi | snowmobile | subway       | trike | car | jet-ski | airplane |

