.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  doctor, police-officer, mechanic, fisherman, social-worker, journalist, nurse
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, baseball, cricket, golf, tennis, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the mechanic is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the social-worker##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is tennis and the doctor##2
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the journalist is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | social-worker | doctor | fisherman | journalist | police-officer | mechanic     | nurse |
| Sport   | cricket   | golf    | weightlifting    | tennis      | baseball  | soccer | water-polo |

