.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, sprite, almond-milk, tea, water, juice
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, basketball, climbing, handball, lacrosse, golf, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person drinking tea##2
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | 7up | soy-milk    | almond-milk | sprite   | water | juice    | tea |
| Sport      | handball | snowboarding | weightlifting    | basketball | lacrosse    | climbing | golf  |

