.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, 7up, iced-tea, sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk
The people have 7 different jobs:  doctor, scientist, firefighter, freelancer, writer, paramedic, bartender
 1. the writer is on the left of the freelancer##1
 2. the doctor is on the left of the firefighter##1
 3. the paramedic is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the writer is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 7. the scientist is on the right of the paramedic##1
 8. the doctor is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking tea##2
11. the writer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | 7up  | sprite   | tea         | coffee     | soy-milk              | almond-milk    | iced-tea     |
| Job        | paramedic | scientist | writer | freelancer | bartender | doctor | firefighter |

