.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, sports, mystery, scientific, time-travel, comedy, family
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, car, airplane, scooter, snowmobile, roller
1. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the scooter##2
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
9. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | scientific     | comedy | time-travel | mystery | family  | superhero |
| Transport     | car | airplane | scooter   | jet-ski     | roller    | van | snowmobile   |

