.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, sprite, juice, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people have 7 different hobbies: fishing, writing, collecting, sudoku, puzzles, chess, camping
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is writing##2
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is chess##2
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | water  | iced-tea       | lemonade         | almond-milk         | juice   | sprite        | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby      | camping | collecting | fishing | puzzles | writing | chess | sudoku  |

