5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is photography##2
8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | photography | fishing       | card-games    | skydiving | board-games | drawing     | traveling       |
