 3. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching action movies and the fan of d&b##2
 4. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching romance movies##2
 5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is the fan of metal##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
10. the fan of indie is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
