 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person eating lemon is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person eating tomato is the person eating tomato##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating banana##1
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
